Kerry Noonan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kerry_Noonan 0 Kerry Noonan (born January 25, 1960) is a professor at Champlain College and a former actress. She was born in NY, but spent most of her life on LA, from where she moved to Vermont in 2008. Kerry_Noonan ( born January_25_,_1960 ) is a_professor at Champlain_College and a_former_actress .
